-   **Development**: Visual Studio Code, Git
-   **Database Management**: pgAdmin / psql
-   **Environments**: Python Virtual Environments (`venv`), NPM
-   **Deployment Readiness**: Modular structure with [.env](file:///c:/Users/vishnu/Desktop/Smart%20and%20Green%20Madurai%20city/backend/.env) configuration for all services.
